{
  "stem": "8072.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My both brothers-- and my mother and father, my three sisters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of my sisters, oldest sister, which is not survived, she even got married during the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were all still home, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't-- no life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just like existence, and hoping the war is going to end, and things are going to get better.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you were just telling yourself that it's got to improve.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- I later on found out that there's no limit to the good, and there's no limit to the bad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at that time, we were always hoping, things are going to get better, because you said, this is the worst.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This can't get any worse, can't get any worse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it got worse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when-- by the time you got 1942, they liquidated the whole town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had heard about liquidation, ghettos, things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But since it was a small town-- I guess they started with the largest cities first, and then they came down to the smaller.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they liquidated the whole town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of my two sisters, they went in hiding at the-- on a farm, at the farmers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the rest of us, where we were liquidated, was my-- we were taken to an assembly into town-- a big field, like a football field, with all your belongings, whatever you could carry.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from there, they were sorted out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My two brothers and myself were sent to one camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother, and my grandmother, and my sister was sent to another camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My dad was sent to another camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We wound up-- my two brothers and myself-- wound up in a camp which was called, Prokocim.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was near Krakow.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
